titleInfo.title: Letter from Henry Willock, Second Assistant to H M Mission, at Bushire, to Lieutenant William Bruce, Acting Resident at Bushire

mods.abstract: Letter from Henry Willock, Second Assistant to H M Mission, at Bushire, to Lieutenant William Bruce, Acting Resident at Bushire, acknowledging the receipt of a letter on the same date and confirming that it will be forwarded, as requested.
